Since the first beta, we've done many changes to the base Terminaux input system to improve performance and reliability.

You are testing the second beta version of Terminaux 7.0, which was released on June 12th, 2025.

### Changes

This release contains a variety of changes, including, but not limited to:

- `[+]` Added Panel and Markup conversion
- `[+]` Added the Hue, White, and Black (HWB) color model
- `[*]` Made significant improvements to the input system
- `[*]` Made TUIs more mouse friendly
- `[*]` Improved performance of the selection TUIs
- `[*]` Improved RTL logical-to-visual mapping
- `[*]` General improvements and bug fixes

Review the commit history if you want to get a deep insight about the changes.

### Disclaimer

Due to the nature of this version of Terminaux, bugs might show up, and some of the features might not make it to the final release.

We can't provide info as to when we're going to make either the next beta version or the final release of this version of Terminaux, but we'll provide them once confirmed.

Participation in the beta program is optional, so you can choose to either try out Terminaux 7.0, or to wait until the final release.

### Feedback?

If you have issues with this version, report to us by [making a new issue ticket](https://github.com/Aptivi/Terminaux/issues/new).

